@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

node "Developer Machine (macOS)" {
  node "Frontend Dev Server" {
    artifact "Vite + React\nhttp://localhost:5173" as Front
  }

  node "Backend Dev Server" {
    artifact "FastAPI + Uvicorn\nhttp://127.0.0.1:8000" as Back
    artifact "Swagger UI\n/docs" as Swagger
  }

  database "JSON Test Data\nbackend/app/data/test_data.json" as JsonRuntime
  database "JSON Baseline\nbackend/app/data/test_data.default.json" as JsonBase
  database "PostgreSQL (optional)" as Pg
}

Front --> Back : REST/JSON over HTTP
Swagger --> Back : OpenAPI execution
Back --> JsonRuntime : read/write test data
Back --> JsonBase : reset baseline load
Back --> Pg : DB health + optional runtime DB usage
@enduml
